dataset.name: archive_remote
dataset.sql: SELECT SUBSTRING(djbh,3,4) as ndd,SUBSTRING(djbh,7,2) as yff,lymd,sum(cast(lyrc as int)) as rc,sum(cast(lyjc as int)) as jc,sum(cast(lyjac as int)) as jac from archive_remote group by SUBSTRING(djbh,3,4),SUBSTRING(djbh,7,2),lymd ORDER BY SUBSTRING(djbh,3,4),SUBSTRING(djbh,7,2);
